          "en": "Muhammad ibn 'Ali Majiluwayh (may Allah have mercy on him) narrated to us. He said: Muhammad ibn Yahya al-'Attar narrated to us from Muhammad ibn Ahmad ibn Yahya ibn 'Imran al-Ash'ari from al-Hasan ibn Musa al-Khashab from Ghiyath ibn Kulub from Ishaq ibn 'Ammar from al-Sadiq Ja'far ibn Muhammad from his father from his forefathers (peace be upon them).",
